title: Mazer in Prison, Pretty Boy & Cheater by Orson Scott Card
description:
This torrent contains three separate audiobooks

- Mazer in Prison

- Pretty Boy

- Cheater

Three short stories in the "ender's game" universe. These were originally posted in Orson Scott Card's web magazine known as the "InterGalactic Medicine Show". 

This was extremely difficult to find and is pretty rare on the internet in audiobook form, so please, if you enjoy this series, seed and help keep it alive for others to enjoy! Thanks!
